# UI templates

HTML source lives in **partials**, assembled into `static/index.html`:

```bash
python scripts/build_ui.py
```

## Layout

```
presentation/static/
  partials/
    layout/head.html, scripts.html
    sidebar.html
    pages/screener.html, opportunity.html, orders.html, settings.html
    opportunity/topbar.html, ex-info-row.html, strategy-table.html,
                params.html, orders-panel.html, chart.html, order-books.html
  css/app.css          # visual match to maket/index.html
  js/core/             # ws_client, dom, delta_router
  js/render/           # per-screen render + delta handlers
  index.html           # build output — do not edit by hand
```

## Rules

1. **No hardcoded market data** in partials — placeholders `—` until WS snapshot.
2. No inline `style="..."` except dynamic values in JS (or layout classes in CSS).
3. Visual reference: `maket/index.html` (design mockup only).
4. Data channel: WebSocket snapshot + delta — `specs/001-mockup-ui/contracts/ws-ui-protocol.md`.

Forbidden: editing `index.html` directly; `import streamlit`; regex port from maket.
